             <property name="whatsThis">
              <string>&lt;p&gt;Each interface of the firewall must have security level associated with it.&lt;br&gt;
Security level can be any number between 0 and 100, 0 being least secure and 100 being most secure levels. Interface with security level 0 ususally serves Internet connection.&lt;/p&gt;</string>
